## 4. VM Changes Required

### 4.1 New Syscalls

| ID | Name | Args | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `0x26` | `GET_CODE_HASH` | `a0=addr_ptr` вҶ’ `a0=hash_ptr` | Get code hash of address |
| `0x27` | `ROLE_CHECK` | `a0=role_id, a1=addr_ptr` вҶ’ `a0=bool` | Check if address has role |
| `0x28` | `ROLE_GRANT` | `a0=role_id, a1=addr_ptr` | Grant role to address |
| `0x29` | `ROLE_REVOKE` | `a0=role_id, a1=addr_ptr` | Revoke role from address |
| `0x2A` | `RESOURCE_LOCK` | `a0=resource_id` | Lock resource for linear type |
| `0x2B` | `RESOURCE_UNLOCK` | `a0=resource_id` | Unlock resource |
| `0x2C` | `DEBUG_LOG` | `a0=msg_ptr, a1=msg_len` | Debug-mode logging |
| `0x2D` | `GET_CHAIN_ID` | вҶ’ `a0=chain_id` | Get current chain ID |
| `0x2E` | `BASEFEE` | вҶ’ `a0=basefee_ptr` | Get block base fee |
| `0x2F` | `PREVRANDAO` | вҶ’ `a0=randao_ptr` | Get previous RANDAO |

### 4.2 Extended Memory Layout

```
Current (640 KB):
  0x00000 - 0x0FFFF  Code      (64 KB)
  0x10000 - 0x4FFFF  Heap      (256 KB)
  0x50000 - 0x6FFFF  Stack     (128 KB)
  0x70000 - 0x8FFFF  Calldata  (128 KB)
  0x90000 - 0x9FFFF  Return    (64 KB)

Proposed (1 MB вҖ” still fits L2 cache):
  0x00000 - 0x1FFFF  Code      (128 KB)  вҖ” larger contracts
  0x20000 - 0x6FFFF  Heap      (320 KB)  вҖ” more working memory
  0x70000 - 0x8FFFF  Stack     (128 KB)  вҖ” unchanged
  0x90000 - 0xAFFFF  Calldata  (128 KB)  вҖ” unchanged
  0xB0000 - 0xCFFFF  Return    (128 KB)  вҖ” larger return data
  0xD0000 - 0xDFFFF  Scratch   (64 KB)   вҖ” NEW: compiler temp space
  0xE0000 - 0xFFFFF  Debug     (128 KB)  вҖ” NEW: debug info (optional)
```

### 4.3 Enhanced Gas Metering

```zig
// New gas costs for ZephyrLang features
pub const ROLE_CHECK_GAS: u64 = 200;     // Role verification
pub const ROLE_GRANT_GAS: u64 = 5000;    // Role state change
pub const RESOURCE_LOCK_GAS: u64 = 100;  // Resource tracking
pub const DEBUG_LOG_GAS: u64 = 0;        // Free in debug mode, disabled in prod
pub const CHAIN_ID_GAS: u64 = 2;         // Cheap env read
pub const BASEFEE_GAS: u64 = 2;          // Cheap env read
```

### 4.4 Contract Metadata Storage

```zig
// In HostEnv вҖ” new fields for ZephyrLang runtime
contract_abi: ?[]const u8,          // JSON ABI for runtime reflection
source_map: ?[]const SourceMapping,  // PC вҶ’ source line for debugging
role_registry: RoleRegistry,         // Per-contract role assignments
resource_locks: ResourceTracker,     // Linear type enforcement
```

