## 5. Solidity вҶ’ ZephyrLang Transpiler

### 5.1 Architecture

```
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ    в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ    в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ    в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ Solidity .solв”Ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв–¶в”Ӯ Existing Parser    в”Ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв–¶в”Ӯ SolвҶ’Zeph Mapper  в”Ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв–¶в”Ӯ .zeph file в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ              в”Ӯ    в”Ӯ (tools/transpiler/ в”Ӯ    в”Ӯ (syntax transformв”Ӯ    в”Ӯ            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ              в”Ӯ    в”Ӯ  parser.zig)       в”Ӯ    в”Ӯ  + feature map)  в”Ӯ    в”Ӯ            в”Ӯ
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ    в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ    в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ    в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
```

**Key**: We already have a full Solidity parser ([tools/transpiler/parser.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/tools/transpiler/parser.zig), 997 lines). The transpiler reuses it and generates `.zeph` output instead of [.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/vm/vm.zig).

### 5.2 Mapping Rules

| Solidity | ZephyrLang | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `pragma solidity ^0.8.0;` | `pragma zephyr ^1.0;` | Version mapping |
| `contract X is Y, Z { }` | `contract X is Y, Z { }` | Identical |
| `mapping(address => uint)` | `mapping(address => uint256)` | Identical |
| `uint` | `uint256` | Explicit sizing |
| `require(cond, "msg")` | `require(cond, "msg")` | Identical |
| `msg.sender` | `msg.sender` | Identical |
| `block.timestamp` | `block.timestamp` | Identical |
| `keccak256(abi.encode(...))` | `keccak256(abi.encode(...))` | Identical |
| `abi.encodeWithSelector(...)` | `abi.encodeWithSelector(...)` | Identical |
| Inline assembly (EVM) | `assembly { /* risc-v */ }` | **Needs manual review** |
| `selfdestruct(addr)` | **REMOVED** вҖ” emit event + drain | Security improvement |
| OpenZeppelin imports | Native equivalents | `import "@oz/..."` |

### 5.3 Automatic Enhancements During Transpilation

```zephyr
// INPUT (Solidity):
contract Vault {
    mapping(address => uint256) balances;
    bool locked;
    function withdraw(uint256 amount) external {
        require(!locked);
        locked = true;
        require(balances[msg.sender] >= amount);
        (bool ok,) = msg.sender.call{value: amount}("");
        require(ok);
        balances[msg.sender] -= amount;
        locked = false;
    }
}

// OUTPUT (ZephyrLang вҖ” auto-enhanced):
contract Vault {
    mapping(address => uint256) balances;
    transient bool _locked;              // вҶҗ Auto: bool вҶ’ transient (saves gas)

    function withdraw(uint256 amount) external nonReentrant {  // вҶҗ Auto: pattern вҶ’ modifier
        require(balances[msg.sender] >= amount, "Insufficient balance");
        balances[msg.sender] -= amount;  // вҶҗ Auto: CEI reordering
        (bool ok,) = msg.sender.call{value: amount}("");
        require(ok, "Transfer failed");  // вҶҗ Auto: error messages added
    }
}
// вҡ пёҸ TRANSPILER WARNING: Reordered state update before external call (CEI pattern)
```

