|---|---|---|
| Lexer (`tools/zephyrc/lexer.zig`) | 3 days | |
| Parser (`tools/zephyrc/parser.zig`) | 1.5 weeks | |
| AST definitions (`tools/zephyrc/ast.zig`) | 2 days | |
| Type checker (`tools/zephyrc/type_check.zig`) | 1 week | |
| Storage layout (`tools/zephyrc/storage_layout.zig`) | 2 days | |

### Phase 2: Code Generation (Weeks 5-8)
| Task | Effort | Owner |
|---|---|---|
| MIR lowering (`tools/zephyrc/mir.zig`) | 1 week | |
| RISC-V codegen (`tools/zephyrc/codegen_riscv.zig`) | 2 weeks | |
| ELF packaging (`tools/zephyrc/elf_emit.zig`) | 3 days | |
| ABI JSON generation (`tools/zephyrc/abi_gen.zig`) | 2 days | |
| Source map generation (`tools/zephyrc/source_map.zig`) | 2 days | |

### Phase 3: VM Enhancements (Weeks 5-6, parallel)
| Task | Effort | Owner |
|---|---|---|
| New syscalls (0x26-0x2F) in [dispatch.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/vm/syscall/dispatch.zig) | 3 days | |
| Extended memory layout in [sandbox.zig](file:///Users/karan/sol2zig/vm/memory/sandbox.zig) | 2 days | |
| Role registry in `HostEnv` | 2 days | |
| Source map loading in contract loader | 1 day | |

### Phase 4: Safety Analysis (Weeks 7-9)
