|---|---|---|
| Reentrancy detector (`tools/zephyrc/safety/reentrancy.zig`) | 1 week | |
| Resource linearity checker | 3 days | |
| Access control verifier | 2 days | |
| Integer overflow proof (compile-time where possible) | 3 days | |

### Phase 5: Standard Library (Weeks 9-12)
