## 8. Comparison Matrix

| Feature | Solidity | Vyper | ZephyrLang |
|---|---|---|---|
| Syntax familiarity | вҳ…вҳ…вҳ…вҳ…вҳ… | вҳ…вҳ…вҳ… | вҳ…вҳ…вҳ…вҳ…вҳ… (Solidity-like) |
| Safety by default | вҳ…вҳ…вҳ… | вҳ…вҳ…вҳ…вҳ… | вҳ…вҳ…вҳ…вҳ…вҳ… |
| Reentrancy protection | Manual | Auto | **Compile-time enforced** |
| Checked arithmetic | Opt-in (0.8+) | Always | **Default + wrapping/sat ops** |
| Access control | Library | N/A | **Language-level roles** |
| Option types (no null) | No | No | **Yes** |
| Resource/linear types | No | No | **Yes** |
| Result types | No | No | **Yes** |
| Pattern matching | No | No | **Yes** |
| Transient storage | EIP-1153 | No | **First-class keyword** |
| Parallel execution hints | No | No | **Yes** |
| Native RISC-V target | No | No | **Yes** |
| Source-level debugging | Limited | Limited | **Full source maps** |
| EVM assembly | Yes | No | **RISC-V assembly** |
| Compile-time compute | No | No | **comptime expressions** |
| Fixed-point math | No | Yes | **Yes** |
| Standard library | OpenZeppelin | Built-in | **Rich built-in std** |

---

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Total estimated effort**: ~16 weeks for a single developer, ~8 weeks with 2 developers working in parallel (compiler + VM/stdlib tracks). Phase 1-2 (lexer/parser/codegen) is the critical path. The existing Solidity parser can be partially reused for the transpiler phase.
